title: Barron's Midterms Election Roundtable on Barron's Live
description: The midterm elections will determine the balance of power in Washington and set the stage for the coming two years. Tax policy, tech regulation and much of President Biden's agenda may hinge on the outcome. Join as Barron's and MarketWatch journalists lead a discussion with political and investing experts on what to watch, what to expect, and what it all means for your portfolio.
